{"data":[{"name":"85:1","price":"1. கோள்கள் நிறைந்த வானத்தின் மீது சத்தியமாக,","arabic":"وَٱلسَّمَآءِ ذَاتِ ٱلۡبُرُوجِ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5910,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wal-samāi dhāti al-burūji ","translations":["By the sky","containing","the constellations","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["wal-samāi","dhāti","al-burūji",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,3450],[2,3450,4120],[3,4120,8325]]}},{"name":"85:2","price":"2. வாக்களிக்கப்பட்ட (மறுமை) நாள் மீது சத்தியமாக,","arabic":"وَٱلۡيَوۡمِ ٱلۡمَوۡعُودِ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5911,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wal-yawmi al-mawʿūdi ","translations":["And the Day","Promised","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["wal-yawmi","al-mawʿūdi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1120],[2,1120,5245]]}},{"name":"85:3","price":"3. சாட்சியின் மீதும், சாட்சி சொல்ல வேண்டிய நாளின் மீதும் சத்தியமாக!","arabic":"وَشَاهِدٖ وَمَشۡهُودٖ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5912,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"washāhidin wamashhūdin ","translations":["And (the) witness","and what is witnessed","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["washāhidin","wamashhūdin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1990],[2,1990,6705]]}},{"name":"85:4","price":"4. அகழுடையவர்கள் அழிக்கப்பட்டார்கள். (அவ்வாறே இம்மக்காவாசிகளும் அழிக்கப்படுவார்கள்.)","arabic":"قُتِلَ أَصۡحَٰبُ ٱلۡأُخۡدُودِ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5913,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"qutila aṣḥābu al-ukh'dūdi ","translations":["Destroyed were","(the) companions","(of) the pit","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["qutila","aṣḥābu","al-ukh'dūdi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,650],[2,650,1610],[3,1610,5935]]}},{"name":"85:5","price":"5. அது, விறகுகள் போட்டெரித்த நெருப்பு (அகழ்).","arabic":"ٱلنَّارِ ذَاتِ ٱلۡوَقُودِ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5914,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"al-nāri dhāti al-waqūdi ","translations":["(Of) the fire","full","(of) the fuel","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["al-nāri","dhāti","al-waqūdi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2120],[2,2120,2760],[3,2760,6735]]}},{"name":"85:6","price":"6. அதன் முன் அவர்கள் உட்கார்ந்து கொண்டிருந்த சமயத்தில்,","arabic":"إِذۡ هُمۡ عَلَيۡهَا قُعُودٞ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5915,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"idh hum ʿalayhā quʿūdun ","translations":["When","they","by it","(were) sitting","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["idh","hum","ʿalayhā","quʿūdun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,450],[2,450,780],[3,780,1790],[4,1790,5425]]}},{"name":"85:7","price":"7. நம்பிக்கையாளர்களை (நெருப்புக் கிடங்கில் போட்டு) நோவினை செய்வதை அவர்கள் (வேடிக்கையாகப்) பார்த்துக் கொண்டுமிருந்தார்கள்.","arabic":"وَهُمۡ عَلَىٰ مَا يَفۡعَلُونَ بِٱلۡمُؤۡمِنِينَ شُهُودٞ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5916,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wahum ʿalā mā yafʿalūna bil-mu'minīna shuhūdun ","translations":["And they","over","what","they were doing","to the believers","witnesses","(7)"],"transliterationArr":["wahum","ʿalā","mā","yafʿalūna","bil-mu'minīna","shuhūdun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,650],[2,650,1330],[3,1330,1730],[4,1730,3040],[5,3040,4550],[6,4550,8555]]}},{"name":"85:8","price":"8. (நம்பிக்கை கொண்ட) அவர்களில் ஒரு குற்றத்தையும் அவர்கள் காணவில்லை. எனினும், மிக்க புகழுடையவனும், (அனைவரையும்) மிகைத்தவனுமாகிய அல்லாஹ்வை அவர்கள் நம்பிக்கை கொண்டதையே அவர்கள் குற்றமாகக் கண்டனர்.","arabic":"وَمَا نَقَمُواْ مِنۡهُمۡ إِلَّآ أَن يُؤۡمِنُواْ بِٱللَّهِ ٱلۡعَزِيزِ ٱلۡحَمِيدِ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5917,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wamā naqamū min'hum illā an yu'minū bil-lahi al-ʿazīzi al-ḥamīdi ","translations":["And not","they resented","[of] them","except","that","they believed","in Allah","the All-Mighty","the Praiseworthy","(8)"],"transliterationArr":["wamā","naqamū","min'hum","illā","an","yu'minū","bil-lahi","al-ʿazīzi","al-ḥamīdi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,630],[2,630,1450],[3,1450,2250],[4,2250,4480],[5,4480,4959],[6,4959,6739],[7,6739,7839],[8,7839,8919],[9,8919,12274]]}},{"name":"85:9","price":"9. வானங்கள், பூமியின் ஆட்சி அவனுக்குரியதே! (அவனை நம்பிக்கை கொண்டதற்காகவே அந்த பாவிகள் அவர்களை நெருப்பில் எறிந்தனர்.) அல்லாஹ்வோ, (இவர்கள் செய்த) அனைத்திற்கும் சாட்சி ஆவான்.","arabic":"ٱلَّذِي لَهُۥ مُلۡكُ ٱلسَّمَٰوَٰتِ وَٱلۡأَرۡضِۚ وَٱللَّهُ عَلَىٰ كُلِّ شَيۡءٖ شَهِيدٌ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5918,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"alladhī lahu mul'ku al-samāwāti wal-arḍi wal-lahu ʿalā kulli shayin shahīdun ","translations":["The One Who","for Him","(is) the dominion","(of) the heavens","and the earth","and Allah","on","every","thing","(is) a Witness","(9)"],"transliterationArr":["alladhī","lahu","mul'ku","al-samāwāti","wal-arḍi","wal-lahu","ʿalā","kulli","shayin","shahīdun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1010],[2,1010,1590],[3,1590,2270],[4,2270,3760],[5,3760,5210],[6,5210,6260],[7,6260,6830],[8,6830,7480],[9,7480,9300],[10,9300,13455]]}},{"name":"85:10","price":"10. ஆகவே, எவர்கள் நம்பிக்கை கொண்ட ஆண்களையும், பெண்களையும் இவ்வாறு துன்புறுத்தி பின்னர், அதைப்பற்றி அவர்கள் (கைசேதப்பட்டு) மன்னிப்புக் கோரவும் இல்லையோ, அவர்களுக்கு நிச்சயமாக நரக வேதனை உண்டு. மேலும், (அவர்கள் நம்பிக்கையாளர்களை நெருப்பிட்டவாறு) அவர்களுக்கும் பொசுக்குகின்ற வேதனையுண்டு.","arabic":"إِنَّ ٱلَّذِينَ فَتَنُواْ ٱلۡمُؤۡمِنِينَ وَٱلۡمُؤۡمِنَٰتِ ثُمَّ لَمۡ يَتُوبُواْ فَلَهُمۡ عَذَابُ جَهَنَّمَ وَلَهُمۡ عَذَابُ ٱلۡحَرِيقِ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5919,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"inna alladhīna fatanū al-mu'minīna wal-mu'mināti thumma lam yatūbū falahum ʿadhābu jahannama walahum ʿadhābu al-ḥarīqi ","translations":["Indeed","those who","persecuted","the believing men","and the believing women","then","not","they repented","then for them","(is the) punishment","(of) Hell","and for them","(is the) punishment","(of) the Burning Fire","(10)"],"transliterationArr":["inna","alladhīna","fatanū","al-mu'minīna","wal-mu'mināti","thumma","lam","yatūbū","falahum","ʿadhābu","jahannama","walahum","ʿadhābu","al-ḥarīqi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1340],[2,1340,2350],[3,2350,2980],[4,2980,4470],[5,4470,6070],[6,6070,7570],[7,7570,7890],[8,7890,8910],[9,8910,9710],[10,9710,10590],[11,10590,12330],[12,12330,13080],[13,13080,13970],[14,13970,17965]]}},{"name":"85:11","price":"11. எவர்கள் நம்பிக்கை கொண்டு நற்செயல்களைச் செய்கிறார்களோ நிச்சயமாக அவர்களுக்கு தொடர்ந்து நீரருவிகள் ஓடிக்கொண்டிருக்கும் சொர்க்கங்களுண்டு. இதுதான் மாபெரும் வெற்றி.","arabic":"إِنَّ ٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُواْ وَعَمِلُواْ ٱلصَّٰلِحَٰتِ لَهُمۡ جَنَّٰتٞ تَجۡرِي مِن تَحۡتِهَا ٱلۡأَنۡهَٰرُۚ ذَٰلِكَ ٱلۡفَوۡزُ ٱلۡكَبِيرُ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5920,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"inna alladhīna āmanū waʿamilū al-ṣāliḥāti lahum jannātun tajrī min taḥtihā al-anhāru dhālika al-fawzu al-kabīru ","translations":["Indeed","those who","believe","and do","the righteous deeds","for them","(will be) Gardens","flow","from","underneath it","the rivers","That","(is) the success","the great","(11)"],"transliterationArr":["inna","alladhīna","āmanū","waʿamilū","al-ṣāliḥāti","lahum","jannātun","tajrī","min","taḥtihā","al-anhāru","dhālika","al-fawzu","al-kabīru",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1600],[2,1600,2640],[3,2640,3830],[4,3830,4530],[5,4530,6020],[6,6020,6590],[7,6590,9359],[8,9359,10229],[9,10229,10859],[10,10859,12079],[11,12079,16139],[12,16139,16969],[13,16969,17799],[14,17799,21594]]}},{"name":"85:12","price":"12. (நபியே! இந்த விஷமிகளைப் பற்றி நீர் கவலைப்பட வேண்டாம். ஏனென்றால்) நிச்சயமாக உமது இறைவனின் பிடி மிக்க கடுமையானது. (அதிலிருந்து அவர்கள் தப்பவே முடியாது.) ","arabic":"إِنَّ بَطۡشَ رَبِّكَ لَشَدِيدٌ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5921,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"inna baṭsha rabbika lashadīdun ","translations":["Indeed","(the) Grip","(of) your Lord","(is) surely strong","(12)"],"transliterationArr":["inna","baṭsha","rabbika","lashadīdun",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1540],[2,1540,2180],[3,2180,2950],[4,2950,6495]]}},{"name":"85:13","price":"13. நிச்சயமாக அவன்தான் (அவர்களை) உற்பத்தி செய்கிறான். (அவர்கள் மரணித்த பின்னரும்) அவர்களை மீளவைப்பான்.","arabic":"إِنَّهُۥ هُوَ يُبۡدِئُ وَيُعِيدُ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5922,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"innahu huwa yub'di-u wayuʿīdu ","translations":["Indeed He","He","originates","and repeats","(13)"],"transliterationArr":["innahu","huwa","yub'di-u","wayuʿīdu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,2170],[2,2170,2500],[3,2500,3470],[4,3470,7205]]}},{"name":"85:14","price":"14. அவன்தான் (நம்பிக்கை கொண்டவர்களை) மிக்க மன்னிப்பவனும், மிக நேசிப்பவனும் ஆவான்.","arabic":"وَهُوَ ٱلۡغَفُورُ ٱلۡوَدُودُ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5923,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"wahuwa al-ghafūru al-wadūdu ","translations":["And He","(is) the Oft-Forgiving","the Most Loving","(14)"],"transliterationArr":["wahuwa","al-ghafūru","al-wadūdu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,510],[2,510,1310],[3,1310,5395]]}},{"name":"85:15","price":"15. (அவன்தான்) அர்ஷுடையவன், மகா கீர்த்தியுடையவன்.","arabic":"ذُو ٱلۡعَرۡشِ ٱلۡمَجِيدُ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5924,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"dhū al-ʿarshi al-majīdu ","translations":["Owner (of)","the Throne","the Glorious","(15)"],"transliterationArr":["dhū","al-ʿarshi","al-majīdu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,230],[2,230,1120],[3,1120,4665]]}},{"name":"85:16","price":"16. தான் விரும்பியதையெல்லாம் செய்யக் கூடியவன்.","arabic":"فَعَّالٞ لِّمَا يُرِيدُ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5925,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"faʿʿālun limā yurīdu ","translations":["Doer","of what","He intends","(16)"],"transliterationArr":["faʿʿālun","limā","yurīdu",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,980],[2,980,1820],[3,1820,4835]]}},{"name":"85:17","price":"17. (நபியே!) அந்தப் படைகளின் செய்தி உமக்கு எட்டியதா? (யாருடைய படைகள்?)","arabic":"هَلۡ أَتَىٰكَ حَدِيثُ ٱلۡجُنُودِ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5926,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"hal atāka ḥadīthu al-junūdi ","translations":["Has","come to you","(the) story","(of) the hosts","(17)"],"transliterationArr":["hal","atāka","ḥadīthu","al-junūdi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,410],[2,410,1220],[3,1220,2060],[4,2060,5365]]}},{"name":"85:18","price":"18. ஃபிர்அவ்ன், ஸமூதுடைய (படைகள்).","arabic":"فِرۡعَوۡنَ وَثَمُودَ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5927,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"fir'ʿawna wathamūda ","translations":["Firaun","and Thamud","(18)"],"transliterationArr":["fir'ʿawna","wathamūda",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1000],[2,1000,4695]]}},{"name":"85:19","price":"19. எனினும், இந்நிராகரிப்பவர்கள் (குர்ஆனைப்) பொய்யாக்குவதிலேயே (முனைந்து) கிடக்கின்றனர்.","arabic":"بَلِ ٱلَّذِينَ كَفَرُواْ فِي تَكۡذِيبٖ","category":["85 (Al-Buruj)","Al-Buruj","Surah Al-Buruj"],"ayahNumber":5928,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":null,"lang":"ta","meta":{"transliteration":"bali alladhīna kafarū fī takdhībin ","translations":["Nay","Those who","disbelieve","(are) in","denial","(19)"],"transliterationArr":["bali","alladhīna","kafarū","fī","takdhībin",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,340],[2,340,1310],[3,1310,